<br />

*** ** * ** ***

Interface to the clipboard service, for placing and retrieving text in the global clipboard.

The ClipboardManager API itself is very simple: it consists of methods to atomically get and set the current primary clipboard data. That data is expressed as a[ClipData](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/ClipData)object, which defines the protocol for data exchange between applications.  

### Developer Guides

For more information about using the clipboard framework, read the[Copy and Paste](https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/clipboard/copy-paste)developer guide.

<br />

